I think it is time for me to post some things I have written over the past year or so. A literary approach is good. It heals. Doc Spatz, read and join with us. I know now you know how things feel.<br><br>
The following is an extract from a larger piece. Yes, I have to say &quot;Copyright 1996, 1997, by Arthur Varanelli, all rights reserved.&quot; It really disgusts me to have to do that. I trust my friends here, but the world is a real place, just like 'Nam.<br><br>
These words are in part metaphor, part feeling. &quot;My old friend&quot; is the War. There is more to this. I may post more down the road.<br>
